trans-unit.source: Creates the theme-specific look for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet*> elements. A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet*> defines the appearance of <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.RadioButton"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: Cria a aparência de tema específico para [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] <> </> *> elementos. Um <> </> *> define a aparência de <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.RadioButton"> </xref> elementos.

trans-unit.source: The actual appearance of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A> is dependent on which theme is active on the user's system.
trans-unit.target: A aparência real do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A>depende de qual tema está ativo no sistema do usuário.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The properties of this class allow [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to set the appearance based on the current theme.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades dessa classe permitem [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para definir a aparência com base no tema atual.

trans-unit.source: In XAML usage, a BulletChrome object element can also have child content, which can be a single <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> that sets the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: No uso XAML, um elemento de objeto BulletChrome também pode ter conteúdo filho, que pode ser um único <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>que define o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the value of IsChecked cannot be set to `null` by user action, but it can be set that way in markup or code.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, o valor de IsChecked não pode ser definido como `null` por usuário ação, mas ele pode ser definido dessa maneira na marcação ou código.
